					 <strong>How my weight changed during the week of quarantine: I share secrets</strong><blockquote><span>  </span><span><i>Hello to all readers! On my channel </i></span><span></span><a><i><b>Julia Fit </b></i></a><span></span><span><i>there are many delicious and useful </i></span><span><i><b>recipes for losing weight </b></i></span><span><i>, as well as a lot of information on </i></span><span><i><b>adequate nutrition weight </b></i></span><span><i>loss !</i></span><span> </span><span><i><b>Subscribe now!</b></i></span><span> </span><span><i>Glad to see you all! And thank you for your feedback in the comments under the articles</i></span><span> </span></blockquote><p><span>It was the second week of quarantine, I jumped on the scales today, and there waaau. Together with the </span><span><b>phone 49.3 kg, </b></span><span>entered the quarantine </span><span><b>50.5 kg. </b></span><span>Height 166 cm. 28 years. The "pear" shape.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>I'm being quarantined</span></figcaption></figure><div><div></div></div><p><span>I generally thought that sitting at home I would be tempted to eat junk food 24/7. After all, there is a husband who eats all this in front of me constantly.</span></p><p><span><b>How did I manage not only not to get better, but even lose weight?</b></span><span> Now tell.</span></p><p><span>In General, all my life I have had different relations with the proverb "out of sight – out of mind". So far, this is not possible within four walls. My husband sits next to Mars, and I sit next to a protein cookie or an Apple. And Oh, my God, how high I </span><span><b>feel</b></span><span>! seriously!</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Snack: coffee with protein cookies</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>My trick in losing weight I would call the following rule: </span><span><b>eat what brings you pleasure.</b></span></p><p><span>Now explain.</span></p><p><span>This rule does not mean that it is already time for you to go call delivery pizzas. Here we mean the following: find something that you will be happy to eat from healthy dishes.</span></p><p><span>Yes, many people like fried potatoes, pizza, pork cutlets with puree, halva and gingerbread, cakes and ice cream. </span><span><b>Is it worth saying in 2020 that these are very high-calorie dishes and products?</b></span><span> And even 300 grams of anything from this is about the amount of food that a person eats at a time without the risk of overeating), so you can immediately get a lot of calories and go into surplus (that is, a situation where a person is gaining weight).</span></p><p><span>Yes, I also love all of the above. And puree, and pizza, and halva. And I can't say that I've completely ruled out such things dishes. But I don't make up my diet from this kind of food. I have them very rarely and only on the day when I really want to "indulge".</span></p><p><span>I feel so much better when the word "FORBIDDEN" doesn't stand between </span><span><b>me and pizza!» </b></span><span>and it's just like a way to have fun.</span></p><p><span>Which takes place in my lives.</span></p><p><span>Which I do not exclude, so as not to go into isolation one "beautiful" day.</span></p><p><span>I have chosen for myself some meals for Breakfast, lunch and dinner, from which I am satisfied and full. Plus I add fruit, nuts, cheese and sometimes protein cookies to the coffee pot. This is to have fun without damage figure.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Breakfast: oatmeal with two types of cottage cheese, banana and protein paste</span></figcaption></figure><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Lunch: chicken drumstick and bulgur with vegetables</span></figcaption></figure><p><span><b>By the way, my opinion, if anyone is interested: I'd rather pay 40 rubles for 1 protein cookies weighing 40 g, than 60 rubles for a pack of cookies from Pyaterochka weighing 200 g. </b></span><span>Less carbohydrates, sugar, flour, and TRANS fat. More protein, nutrition and chances to keep your figure.</span></p><p><span>And to be more precise, the protein cookies I buy do </span><span><b>not contain sugar, flour, or TRANS fat. </b></span><span>In this and it makes sense to buy it.</span></p><p><span><b>My activity...</b></span><span> She wasn't hurt at all. I didn't wind up 30,000 steps before the quarantine, as I am a working person who sits for half a day. So now I can easily get my quota of 10,000 steps within four walls.</span></p><p><span>No, I don't go back and forth. I jump, dance, run on the place. I also have a stepper cardio machine. It perfectly helps to close the daily rate of steps. In General, I could have done it without him.</span></p><p><span><b>I </b></span><span>have training sessions, as before – 4 times a week. Within the apartment and without inventory.</span></p><p><span>There is a set of elastic bands, sometimes I use them. Although last week I didn't use them in training, but I could barely walk a day later. Multi-repetitions very cool worked the entire body. My muscles bled, and I began to sweat. And these feelings after training – this is a very high state!</span></p><p><span><b>As a result: I eat delicious, train for fun, and even with chocolate bars, I don't gain pounds, which I do not forbid myself, but also do not eat every day. Moreover, I even managed to lose a little weight, although there was no such goal)</b></span></p><p><span>How are you doing in quarantine? Movies or TV shows with smartphones?</span></p><h2><span><b>I have a lot of interesting articles and delicious recipes for losing weight on my blog:</b></span></h2><blockquote><span><i>How to count I wrote my </i></span><span></span><span><i><b>personal calorie intake for weight </b></i></span><span></span><span><i>loss </i></span><span></span><span></span><a><i>HERE </i></a><span><i>.</i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span><i><b>How to lose weight in the </b></i></span><span></span><span><i>stomach-click </i></span><span></span><span></span><a><i>HERE </i></a><span><i>to read the article.</i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span><i>Two options </i></span><span></span><span><i><b>for dinner for those who lose weight</b></i></span><span><i>: </i></span><span></span><span></span><a><i>here </i></a><span></span><a></a><span><i>and </i></span><span></span><span></span><a><i>here </i></a><span><i>.</i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span><i><b>Recipe for lush cheesecakes that do not fall apart </b></i></span><span></span><span></span><a><i>HERE </i></a><span><i>. Flour at least!</i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span><i>And in</i></span><span> </span><span></span><a><i>THIS</i></a><span></span><a> </a><span><i>in this article, I have collected </i></span><span></span><span><i><b>11 Breakfast recipes for weight loss </b></i></span><span><i>. You will definitely like it!</i></span></blockquote><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><p><span></span></p><p><span></span><span></span><a><b>Julia Fit blog </b></a><span>(click to subscribe).</span></p><blockquote><span><i><b>Share my recipes, life hacks and share other information with your friends in social networks!</b></i></span></blockquote><p><span><i><b>Health to all</b></i></span></p><div></div>
					
